Design 1 positive, 1 negative and 1 edge test case for following public api at zomato.com
{Launch https://developers.zomato.com/documentation#!/common/categories}
This API is offered by zomato to get a list of categories. List of all restaurants categorized under a particular restaurant type can be obtained using /Search API with Category ID as inputs

CURL:
curl -X GET --header "Accept: application/json"
            --header "user-key: 7b8c2002a92c21109f1dfd2808ea50e1" "https://developers.zomato.com/api/v2.1/categories"


Model:
[
  {
    "category_id": "3",
    "category_name": "Nightlife"
  }
]

Success response:
{
  "categories": [
    {
      "categories": {
