-----------*------------*--------------------
Positive test cases:
S.Nos: TC_01
    Description: Verify the API behaviour in case we pass integer for any string input param/object in json
                 Actual result: API returns 200 response code with valid JSON response
                       Expected result: API should return 200 response code with valid JSON response
                             Status: PASS

S.Nos: TC_02
    Description: Verify the respone in case we pass integer for any string input param/object in json
                 Actual result: API response has an category_id with value 1 and name as delivery
                       Expected result: API should return a response with category_id=1 and name as delviery
                             Status: PASS
-----------*------------*--------------------
Negative test cases:
S.Nos: TC_01
    Description: Verify the API behaviour in case we don't pass any of the mandatory param/object in resp json
                                  Actual result: API returns 5xx response code with valid error message configured for tha error code
                                        Expected result: API should return 5xx response code with valid error message
                                              Status: PASS

S.Nos: TC_02
    Description: Verify the API behaviour in case client sends incorrect request
                                  Actual result: API returns 4xx response code with valid error message configured for tha error code
                                        Expected result: API should return 4xx response code with valid error message
                                              Status: PASS
-----------*------------*--------------------
Edge test cases:
S.Nos: TC_01
    Description: Verify the API behaviour in case we pass any out of bound value as per the datatype of any of the param
                                                   Actual result: API returns 5xx/4xxx response code with valid error message configured for tha error code
                                                         Expected result: API should return 5xx/4xx response code with valid error message
                                                               Status: PASS
